modName: Dual Sheath Redux - EWIs True Weaponry of Viscounts and Sirrahs
summary: Dual Sheath Patch for EWIs VWS mod
descriptionHtml:
I'm back with another DSR patch.. hope this one is enjoyed by all

Requirements -
EWIs True Weaponry of Viscounts and Sirrahs - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51032/?
Obviously Neovalen's Dual Sheath Redux - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34155/?

Permission to alter this patch must be obtained from both Neovalen and EWI as all assets were created by them. (I've only altered with their permission to make it work)

Enjoy and be sure to endorse the main files if you like this. Without them this patch would not be possible.

P.S. Any glitches or issues, leave a post or message me, i was building my own mod while doing this one too, so was half distracted, but should work just fine.
